name: Universe #244 x Bowl Head
description:
Universe #244 x Bowl Head - Bowl Head was far away from the universe it belonged. Wandering aimlessly, it came across Klesete. Klesete's many mirrored worlds reflected all of the void back to the Bowl Head. In it's search for it's home, Bowl Head fell deeper and deeper, into the reflections of the universe. Now it exists in the reflections, forever.
--
Rasa Kolko Collab
9 Dec. '21
